trailingComments.value:
*
 * Converts val to array. If val is array return it.
 * @param {*} val
 * @return {Array}
 * @example
 *
 *      toArray([1,2,3]) // => [1,2,3]
 *      toArray(5) // => [5]
 *      toArray('test') // => ['test']
 *      toArray(['test']) // => ['test']
 *      toArray(null) // => []
 *      toArray(undefined) // => []
